Nigerian filmmaker Dimeji Ajibola returns with an action-packed film Ratnik. Ratnik teaser is filled with suspense, superhero characters that are bound to put us on the edge. Judging from the teaser, the 3D effect is not just impressive, it takes on Hollywood style. The film features Bolanle Ninalowo, Osas Ighodaro, Meg Otanwa, Karibi Fubara, Ani Iyoho and Adunni Ade. Check on it: 